Package: plasma-applet-qalculate
Architecture: any
Depends: libqalculate21, plasma-framework, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Qalculate applet for KDE plasma desktop
 A calculator widget for the KDE Plasma 5 desktop environment which uses the
 Qalculate! library to provide lots of features like unit calculation and
 currency conversion. It provides easy one-click access to the Qalculate! GTK
 calculator application and records a history of past calculation results for
 convenient copy/pasting.
